{"tid":1041141,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道的 每次乾泣過後 都可以苟存在世上多一秒","createTime":"2019-02-28T15:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T09:21:37.000Z","uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47f8d33222a3e08a20c753a4df59955fe545c6f7","tid":1041141,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"到底人喺咩時候 具備咗啲咩條件 <br />\n先可以向其他人提出要求？？<br />\n<br />\n我係個有求必應嘅人 返份pt可以返到成個full time噉<br />\n時間任人編 亦唔敢剔假 一個電話嚟 可以走堂頂埋更 <br />\n朋友叫我幫佢做嘅嘢 我都好少拒絕<br />\n<br />\n但點解換轉係自己 明明有需要但都會羞於開口？<br />\n對上一個女朋友係噉<br />\n依家喱個都係噉<br />\n想趁放假有機會可以一齊訓<br />\n但就係開唔到口 一諗到自己噉柒又冇錢冇條件<br />\n賴蛤蟆想食天鵝肉<br />\n就唔敢提出喱個要求<br />\n而女朋友又好似察覺到喱樣嘢 <br />\n但又冇比咩反應<br />\n我唯有將喱份心意硬生吞落肚 但真係好唔開心"},{"pid":"22347fef5f697c37673d3aa593c3fdc137d8b97d","tid":1041141,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7624bc33594afa3dc6a0ebea6cb2d92460c05933","tid":1041141,"uid":183752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"你就好 有女朋友"},{"pid":"496e3217be3895c17f7830317775483511e7ad92","tid":1041141,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7624bc33594afa3dc6a0ebea6cb2d92460c05933","tid":1041141,"uid":183752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"你就好 有女朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 會有的<br />\n我喱啲雙失青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你幫我推post呀"},{"pid":"978bfb20400af9a71386385914603fb8ec13876c","tid":1041141,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:11:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"18430d69d7ea53452230c16704ce247b86c0d129","tid":1041141,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:11:22.00